 524:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/print.c ****     allocation is not packed.
 525:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/print.c **** 
 526:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/print.c **** --*/
 527:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/print.c **** {
